<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śakavarṣaṁbulu 1199 gunēṁṭṭi Uttarāyaṇasaṁkrā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṁttinimittyamuna kṣīrārāmīśvaraśrīmahādēvaraku sū
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rāsāni Araviṁddanāyuṁḍu tama taṁḍri tallapanēni
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kiṁ dama talli nāmasāniki dharmmuvugā Akhaṁḍadīpā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>nakuṁ beṭṭina mōdālu 50 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> I divya kṣētramu palupa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṛti polānanu Onamāseṟuvu paḍmaṭaṁ badēṁdumu
<lb n="7"/>sēnuI seṟvu Uttarānaṁ badēṁdumu sēnu berasi kha
<lb n="8"/>1 na 10 sēnu vīniṁ jēkoni seṁganabōyini koḍku A
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nnebōyuṁḍu nitya naṁdimānika māneṁḍēsi neyi
<lb n="10"/>naḍapaṁgālavāṁḍu Ācaṁdrārkkastāyigā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svadattaṁ
<lb n="11"/>paradattaṁ vā yō <unclear>ha</unclear>rēta vasuṁdharaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śaṣṭivarṣasahasrāṇi viṣṭā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>yāṁ jāyatē krimi[ḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>*] likhitaṁ saraṇōju <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied><note n="61-1">On another face of the pillar are the following syllables:— śrīrāmēśvaruniki Aḍḍapēriśeṭṭi Accama komāruḍu vekkana śēviṁccenu in four lines.</note>
</p>

